    <name>Expert Learning Characteristics: Reflection with your learners.</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;You watched this video earlier in the course.&amp;nbsp; Now share this video with your adult
learners and have them:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reflect on the game-changing nature of technology on their learning&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Review the &lt;span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/Practices%20of%20Expert%20Learners_0.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;UDL
Practices of Expert Learners&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Identify the expert learning characteristics the observed.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Identify the expert learning characteristics they see in themselves and/or each other.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Identify a characteristic that is most challenging for them and brainstorm how they might work to grow and strengthen that characteristic.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Video Title:&amp;nbsp;Game-changing Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 4min 10sec&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/OCTAE%20Transcripts%20Module%207%20Improving%20Systems%20%281%29.docx" target="_blank"&gt;Downloadable Transcripts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/DxzK8kRL5tM" target="_blank"&gt;Game-changing Technology (video)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Go back to the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@COURSEVIEWBYID*296@$#section-5" target="_blank"&gt;Try It Yourself Section&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a list of all Try it Yourself Options.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider-wave-1.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
